update `cates` set `lft` = CASE
WHEN `lft` BETWEEN 48 AND 48 THEN `lft` + 50 - 48
WHEN `lft` BETWEEN 49 AND 50 THEN `lft` + 48 - 49
ELSE `lft` END, `rgt` = CASE
WHEN `rgt` BETWEEN 48 AND 48 THEN `rgt` + 50 - 48
WHEN `rgt` BETWEEN 49 AND 50 THEN `rgt` + 48 - 49
ELSE `rgt` END, `parent_id` = CASE
WHEN `id` = '26' THEN '1'
ELSE `parent_id` END, `updated_at` = '2016-10-24 16:55:39' where (`lft` between '48' and '50' or `rgt` between '48' and '50') order by `cates`.`lft` asc
